Echo,StreamServer,is,a,real,time,API,that,gives,companies,the,ability,to,aggregate,and,control,content,and,activity,from,their,sites,social,networks,applications,and,more,into,one,real,time,database,This,information,can,be,used,to,output,dynamic,web,pages,of,social,content,With,the,API,users,can,capture,process,remix,and,stream,real,time,activity,data,The,API,uses,RESTful,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON